e="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime"></div></div></div></div></div></div><h2 id="how-to-get-your-free-amazon-kindle-e-books-in-september">如何在 9 月份获取免费的 Amazon Kindle 电子书</h2><p>转到<a href="https://zdcs.link/BYLW1?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Deals&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=First%20Reads%20landing%20page&amp;short_url=BYLW1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">“首次阅读”登录页面</a>可查看本月可用电子书的完整列表。一旦您发现一本看起来有趣的书，请单击“首次阅读”登录页面上的“立即购买”按钮。确保您没有被重定向到 Kindle 或 Amazon 移动应用程序，因为您不会在那里看到免费图书选项；相反，请使用手机或计算机上的互联网浏览器。</p><p>确保您没有点击“预购...”按钮，因为这会引导您付款；相反，请单击该书亚马逊页面“首次阅读”横幅下的“免费阅读”或“一键立即购买”按钮（不用担心，我们不会向您收费）。这会将电子书直接发送到链接到您的亚马逊帐户的 Kindle。</p><p>您可以从下面的屏幕截图中看到它应该是什么样子。 </p><div class="eloquent-imagery-image"><div class="flex justify-center"><img class="border border-gray-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HN0ZP8S1KSR9CY579D4F5JF6/images-1.fill.size_367x750.v1706208994.png" alt="来自网络浏览器的手机上亚马逊页面的屏幕截图，显示“免费阅读”按钮。" width="367" height="750" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HN0ZP8S1KSR9CY579D4F5JF6/images-1.fill.size_800x1637.v1706208994.png 800w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HN0ZP8S1KSR9CY579D4F5JF6/images-1.fill.size_1400x2865.v1706208994.png 1400w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HN0ZP8S1KSR9CY579D4F5JF6/images-1.fill.size_2000x4093.v1706208994.png 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px"></div><div class="mt-2"><span class="mt-2 font-akshar text-sm tracking-wide"></span><span class="text-xs inline-block text-gray-600">图片来源：丹尼尔·奥罗佩萨</span></div></div><p>当您看到“谢谢，[您的名字]！”时，您就会知道自己做对了。订单摘要表明电子书正在自动发送到 Kindle 云阅读器。</p><h2 id="free-amazon-kindle-e-books-available-in-september-2024">免费 Amazon Kindle 电子书将于 2024 年 9 月推出</h2><p>这个月，您可以从八本 Kindle 电子书中选择一本，并获得<a href="https://zdcs.link/QGVql8?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Deals&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=Jane%20Green&amp;short_url=QGVql8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开">简·格林 (Jane Green</a> ) 所著的“短读奖励”《 <a href="https://zdcs.link/z3bJ3R?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Deals&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=When%20We%20Were%20Friends%2C&amp;short_url=z3bJ3R&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="在新窗口中打开"><em>当我们是朋友</em></a>》 <em>。</em></p><p>亚马逊在标题上方注明了每本书的类型，提供了一种快速缩小选择范围的方法。如果您将鼠标悬停在“立即购买”按钮下的“查看编辑注释”上，您将能够阅读挑选该书的初读编辑的简短描述。</p><p>以下是您 2024 年 9 月的选择： </p><div class="shadow-b-2 mb-4 rounded-md border-2 border-[#F0F0F0] px-6 py-2 shadow-lg md:px-12" role="region" aria-label="Products List" x-data="{ showMore: false }"><div class="flex w-full flex-col flex-nowrap justify-center gap-2 text-black no-underline md:order-2 md:gap-y-6"><div class="flex flex-col justify-between gap-y-2 md:w-full md:gap-y-1"><div class="block font-sans text-xs font-semibold capitalize leading-3 text-gray-900 md:leading-4">简·格林所著的附赠短读。 </div><div class="block w-fit cursor-pointer font-akshar text-lg font-medium leading-5 text-brand-green duration-200 ease-in-out hover:text-brand-green-700 md:text-xl md:leading-6">当我们是朋友时：一个短篇故事</div></div><div class="hidden md:flex md:justify-between md:gap-x-4"><div class="w-full mb-0 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center font-sans leading-4 text-black"><div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-1 md:justify-start"><span class="font-bold"><span class="font-medium">亚马逊</span>1.99 美元</span></div></div><button class="flex justify-center items-center w-full bg-brand-green text-white text-base font-sans font-medium rounded-md hover:bg-brand-green-700 hover:cursor-pointer md:text-sm hidden self-end h-12 max-w-[10rem] duration-200 ease-in-out hover:bg-brand-green-700 md:flex md:h-10">获得优惠</button></div></div><div class="flex aspect-video h-[90px] shrink-0 items-